817
01:08:51,880 --> 01:08:52,840
[SPEAKER_00] ne znam zašto me kokoš postavio.

818
01:08:52,840 --> 01:08:53,220
[SPEAKER_00] Kokoš.

819
01:08:53,220 --> 01:08:57,479
[SPEAKER_00] Seks,

820
01:08:57,479 --> 01:08:58,800
[SPEAKER_00] možda kao

821
01:08:58,800 --> 01:09:01,199
[SPEAKER_00] metoda nekog prije spavanja.

822
01:09:01,199 --> 01:09:02,619
[SPEAKER_01] Sigurno ima studija

823
01:09:02,619 --> 01:09:03,579
[SPEAKER_01] koji to pokazuju.

824
01:09:03,579 --> 01:09:04,119
[SPEAKER_01] Ja moram pitanje,

825
01:09:04,119 --> 01:09:05,239
[SPEAKER_01] nisam detaljno gledao.

826
01:09:05,239 --> 01:09:06,140
[SPEAKER_01] To,

827
01:09:06,140 --> 01:09:07,520
[SPEAKER_01] ono što ti mogu reći je,

828
01:09:07,520 --> 01:09:08,659
[SPEAKER_01] što se tiče toga,

829
01:09:08,659 --> 01:09:10,279
[SPEAKER_01] krevet bi trebao biti

830
01:09:10,279 --> 01:09:11,840
[SPEAKER_01] za intimu i za spavanje.

831
01:09:11,840 --> 01:09:13,039
[SPEAKER_01] Ne za gledanje Netflixa,

832
01:09:13,039 --> 01:09:14,619
[SPEAKER_01] ne za rad na kompiteru,

833
01:09:14,699 --> 01:09:16,800
[SPEAKER_01] jer treba asocijirati sobu

834
01:09:16,800 --> 01:09:18,159
[SPEAKER_01] i krevet sa spavanjem.

835
01:09:18,159 --> 01:09:19,020
[SPEAKER_01] Intimom.

836
01:09:19,020 --> 01:09:21,220
[SPEAKER_01] I treba izaći iz sobe ujutro

837
01:09:21,220 --> 01:09:22,399
[SPEAKER_01] i raditi negdje drugdje.

838
01:09:22,399 --> 01:09:23,220
[SPEAKER_01] To je ovako

839
01:09:23,220 --> 01:09:24,439
[SPEAKER_01] i anegdotalni,

840
01:09:24,439 --> 01:09:26,500
[SPEAKER_01] ali i znanstveni razlog.

841
01:09:26,500 --> 01:09:27,100
[SPEAKER_01] Tako, nažalost,

842
01:09:27,100 --> 01:09:28,300
[SPEAKER_01] na ovo pitanje ti ne mogu odgovoriti.

843
01:09:28,300 --> 01:09:29,640
[SPEAKER_01] Zvuči da bi pomoglo,

844
01:09:29,640 --> 01:09:31,159
[SPEAKER_00] ali ovo je nekako...

845
01:09:31,159 --> 01:09:31,939
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim da opusti.

846
01:09:31,939 --> 01:09:33,920
[SPEAKER_01] Može biti.

847
01:09:33,920 --> 01:09:34,420
[SPEAKER_00] Čini mi se.

848
01:09:34,420 --> 01:09:35,340
[SPEAKER_00] Onako glajički.

849
01:09:35,340 --> 01:09:38,239
[SPEAKER_01] Ovo je anegdotalni nekakav dokaz.

850
01:09:38,239 --> 01:09:38,979
[SPEAKER_01] Ja kažem,

851
01:09:38,979 --> 01:09:39,960
[SPEAKER_01] sigurno postoje studija,

852
01:09:39,960 --> 01:09:41,479
[SPEAKER_01] jer svakakve studije postoje

853
01:09:41,479 --> 01:09:42,239
[SPEAKER_01] i ja sam siguran,

854
01:09:42,600 --> 01:09:43,779
[SPEAKER_01] ono što treba ovdje reći je,

855
01:09:43,779 --> 01:09:44,819
[SPEAKER_01] što se tiče znanosti,

856
01:09:44,819 --> 01:09:45,739
[SPEAKER_01] baš kad smo na toj temi,

857
01:09:45,739 --> 01:09:46,439
[SPEAKER_01] vrlo kratko.

858
01:09:46,439 --> 01:09:49,460
[SPEAKER_01] Ne treba vjerovati svemu što je objavljeno.

859
01:09:49,460 --> 01:09:50,659
[SPEAKER_01] To je za početak.

860
01:09:50,659 --> 01:09:53,220
[SPEAKER_01] I kad vidim bilo gdje naslove

861
01:09:53,220 --> 01:09:55,399
[SPEAKER_01] i razumijem zašto se to nekad dogodi,

862
01:09:55,399 --> 01:09:56,659
[SPEAKER_01] jer nisu ljudi iz tog polja.

863
01:09:56,659 --> 01:09:58,420
[SPEAKER_01] Ali kad se objavi znanstveni članak,

864
01:09:58,420 --> 01:10:00,140
[SPEAKER_01] to ne znači da je to dogma.

865
01:10:00,140 --> 01:10:02,439
[SPEAKER_01] Hrpa znanstvenih članaka

866
01:10:02,439 --> 01:10:03,720
[SPEAKER_01] se ne može replicirati

867
01:10:03,720 --> 01:10:04,720
[SPEAKER_01] na svih istraživanja.

868
01:10:04,720 --> 01:10:05,979
[SPEAKER_01] I sad je pitanje,

869
01:10:05,979 --> 01:10:07,939
[SPEAKER_01] pa kome ili čemu ću ja vjerovat?

870
01:10:08,439 --> 01:10:09,380
[SPEAKER_01] Budi skeptičan,

871
01:10:09,380 --> 01:10:11,220
[SPEAKER_01] čitaj znanstvene članke,

872
01:10:11,220 --> 01:10:13,220
[SPEAKER_01] ne jedan i ona slijepo vjeroja tome.

873
01:10:13,220 --> 01:10:15,300
[SPEAKER_01] Ako ih je 50 pokazalo isto stvar,

874
01:10:15,300 --> 01:10:17,119
[SPEAKER_01] to vjerojatno je točno.

875
01:10:17,119 --> 01:10:19,300
[SPEAKER_01] Ali koliko znanstvenih članaka

876
01:10:19,300 --> 01:10:21,039
[SPEAKER_01] u najboljim časopisima svijeta

877
01:10:21,039 --> 01:10:22,300
[SPEAKER_01] se ne može replicirati,

878
01:10:22,300 --> 01:10:24,100
[SPEAKER_01] zapravo tragično s te strane.

879
01:10:24,100 --> 01:10:26,640
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ne kažem znanstvenici iz mišljaju,

880
01:10:26,640 --> 01:10:28,720
[SPEAKER_01] nego jednostavno uvjeti

881
01:10:28,720 --> 01:10:31,420
[SPEAKER_01] koji mogu biti toliko glupavi,

882
01:10:31,420 --> 01:10:33,500
[SPEAKER_01] a kazat ću sad jedan tako glupa uvjet

883
01:10:33,500 --> 01:10:35,199
[SPEAKER_01] koji mogu uzrokovati

884
01:10:35,199 --> 01:10:36,939
[SPEAKER_01] da ti ne možeš replicirati određenu studiju.

885
01:10:36,939 --> 01:10:38,119
[SPEAKER_01] Evo ti primjer.

886
01:10:38,119 --> 01:10:40,579
[SPEAKER_01] Na MIT-u koju su učilište u Bostonu,

887
01:10:40,579 --> 01:10:42,699
[SPEAKER_01] ono je udaljeno 15 minuta hoda od Harvarda.

888
01:10:42,699 --> 01:10:44,100
[SPEAKER_01] 15 minuta hoda.

889
01:10:44,100 --> 01:10:46,140
[SPEAKER_01] Imaš miševe, životinje

890
01:10:46,140 --> 01:10:47,899
[SPEAKER_01] koje ljudi testiraju za razne razne stvari.

891
01:10:47,899 --> 01:10:50,840
[SPEAKER_01] Stavili su ih identične uvjete.

892
01:10:50,840 --> 01:10:52,880
[SPEAKER_01] Ista hrana, ista voda,

893
01:10:52,880 --> 01:10:54,699
[SPEAKER_01] ista temperatura zraka itd.

894
01:10:54,699 --> 01:10:56,180
[SPEAKER_01] 15 minuta hoda.

895
01:10:56,180 --> 01:10:58,699
[SPEAKER_01] Kompletno drugačijim crevnim mikrobijom.

896
01:10:58,720 --> 01:11:01,020
[SPEAKER_01] I sad je pitanje,

897
01:11:01,020 --> 01:11:02,520
[SPEAKER_01] kako ćeš provucajavati crevnim mikrobijom

898
01:11:02,520 --> 01:11:03,619
[SPEAKER_01] ako 15 minuta hoda?

899
01:11:03,619 --> 01:11:05,779
[SPEAKER_01] Isti su uvjeti, kompletno drugačiji.

900
01:11:05,779 --> 01:11:07,800
[SPEAKER_01] Ne pokušam pivati po crevnom mikrobijomu,

901
01:11:07,800 --> 01:11:09,319
[SPEAKER_01] ali govorim samo primjer

902
01:11:09,319 --> 01:11:11,739
[SPEAKER_01] koliko je teško replicirati studije

903
01:11:11,739 --> 01:11:13,199
[SPEAKER_01] kad ti ne možeš u istim uvjetima

904
01:11:13,199 --> 01:11:15,460
[SPEAKER_01] imati isti na primjer crevni mikrobijom.

905
01:11:15,460 --> 01:11:17,539
[SPEAKER_01] A kamo li neke kompleksne studije

906
01:11:17,539 --> 01:11:19,960
[SPEAKER_01] koji zahtijevaju razne životinske modele,

907
01:11:19,960 --> 01:11:21,779
[SPEAKER_01] mušice, miševe, crve,

908
01:11:21,779 --> 01:11:23,100
[SPEAKER_01] razne životinske modele,

909
01:11:23,100 --> 01:11:25,359
[SPEAKER_01] to je iznimno teško replicirati.

910
01:11:25,619 --> 01:11:27,819
[SPEAKER_01] I zato nemojmo vjerova svemu što čitamo,

911
01:11:27,819 --> 01:11:30,180
[SPEAKER_01] budimo skeptični, budimo oprezni

912
01:11:30,180 --> 01:11:31,239
[SPEAKER_01] jer je sva što je u svijetu

913
01:11:31,239 --> 01:11:32,600
[SPEAKER_01] i različite, svi su treba reći,

914
01:11:32,600 --> 01:11:34,680
[SPEAKER_01] različite su namjere za što ljudi objavljuju.

915
01:11:34,680 --> 01:11:36,260
[SPEAKER_01] Neki ljudi objavljuje vodat znanost,

916
01:11:36,260 --> 01:11:37,840
[SPEAKER_01] neki ljudi objavljuje što dobili novaci

917
01:11:37,840 --> 01:11:38,500
[SPEAKER_01] moraju objaviti,

918
01:11:38,500 --> 01:11:40,539
[SPEAKER_01] neki ljudi objavljuje zbog drugih razloga

919
01:11:40,539 --> 01:11:41,880
[SPEAKER_01] jer moraju napredovati u znanosti.

920
01:11:41,880 --> 01:11:43,260
[SPEAKER_01] Ne zato što je kvalitetna studija,

921
01:11:43,260 --> 01:11:44,020
[SPEAKER_01] nego moraju napredovati.

922
01:11:44,020 --> 01:11:45,819
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da treba biti jako oprezan.

923
01:11:45,819 --> 01:11:47,159
[SPEAKER_01] Ovo sigurno nije samo u znanosti,

924
01:11:47,159 --> 01:11:48,859
[SPEAKER_01] nego u brojnim sferama,

925
01:11:48,859 --> 01:11:50,359
[SPEAKER_01] samo što ja znam i znanosti,

926
01:11:50,359 --> 01:11:51,840
[SPEAKER_01] a ne znam u drugim sferama.

927
01:11:52,399 --> 01:11:54,680
[SPEAKER_00] Jako iskreno o tebe

928
01:11:54,680 --> 01:11:57,260
[SPEAKER_00] i apsolutno se slažem.

929
01:11:57,260 --> 01:12:01,659
[SPEAKER_00] Objećao sam na početku

930
01:12:01,659 --> 01:12:02,899
[SPEAKER_00] da ćemo malo prokomentirati,

931
01:12:02,899 --> 01:12:03,640
[SPEAKER_00] pa idemo sad.

932
01:12:03,640 --> 01:12:05,680
[SPEAKER_00] Da li si ikak čuo,

933
01:12:05,680 --> 01:12:07,479
[SPEAKER_00] zato ili si možda sad prvi put,

934
01:12:07,479 --> 01:12:08,859
[SPEAKER_00] kad sam ja postao ovo pitanje,

935
01:12:08,859 --> 01:12:09,579
[SPEAKER_00] ono na početku,

936
01:12:09,579 --> 01:12:11,359
[SPEAKER_00] kad sam rekao o čem ćemo razgovarati,

937
01:12:11,359 --> 01:12:13,479
[SPEAKER_00] o Nikuli Tesli.

938
01:12:13,479 --> 01:12:15,380
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim da je osim Nikule Tesli

939
01:12:15,380 --> 01:12:18,020
[SPEAKER_00] bio i još jedan ovako malo čudak,

940
01:12:18,020 --> 01:12:18,460
[SPEAKER_00] recimo,

941
01:12:18,460 --> 01:12:20,720
[SPEAKER_00] koji je znao koristiti tu tehniku,

942
01:12:20,720 --> 01:12:21,340
[SPEAKER_00] da je sjedio,

943
01:12:21,760 --> 01:12:22,920
[SPEAKER_00] znači u stolici,

944
01:12:22,920 --> 01:12:25,560
[SPEAKER_00] držao metalnu kuglu

945
01:12:25,560 --> 01:12:26,859
[SPEAKER_00] i čekao da zaspe.

946
01:12:26,859 --> 01:12:28,720
[SPEAKER_00] Kada je zaspu ta kugla ispala,

947
01:12:28,720 --> 01:12:29,600
[SPEAKER_00] on se odmah probudio.

948
01:12:29,600 --> 01:12:32,680
[SPEAKER_01] Jesam li čuo za Nikulu Teslu

949
01:12:32,680 --> 01:12:33,819
[SPEAKER_01] to točno nisam?

950
01:12:33,819 --> 01:12:34,699
[SPEAKER_01] Ono što sam čuo,

951
01:12:34,699 --> 01:12:36,739
[SPEAKER_01] ja mislim da je bio,

952
01:12:36,739 --> 01:12:38,520
[SPEAKER_01] možda Pablo Picasso,

953
01:12:38,520 --> 01:12:39,739
[SPEAKER_01] ako si to gledao,

954
01:12:39,739 --> 01:12:42,260
[SPEAKER_01] jedan od poznatih slikara je imao,

955
01:12:42,260 --> 01:12:44,119
[SPEAKER_01] mislim da je bila žlica u pitanju.

956
01:12:44,119 --> 01:12:45,800
[SPEAKER_01] Da je držao žlicu u ruci,

957
01:12:45,800 --> 01:12:46,760
[SPEAKER_01] na stolu,

958
01:12:46,760 --> 01:12:47,819
[SPEAKER_01] i kad bi zaspao,

959
01:12:47,819 --> 01:12:48,640
[SPEAKER_01] mišići bi se opustili,

960
01:12:48,640 --> 01:12:50,119
[SPEAKER_01] ta žlica bi pala sa stola

961
01:12:50,119 --> 01:12:51,300
[SPEAKER_01] i onda bi ga probudila.

962
01:12:51,300 --> 01:12:52,979
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim da sam to čuo,

963
01:12:52,979 --> 01:12:54,020
[SPEAKER_01] ali ovo je slično nekako,

964
01:12:54,020 --> 01:12:54,819
[SPEAKER_01] ono, direction,

965
01:12:54,819 --> 01:12:56,680
[SPEAKER_01] što bi rekli u smjeru.

966
01:12:56,680 --> 01:12:57,520
[SPEAKER_01] To me je,

967
01:12:57,520 --> 01:12:58,359
[SPEAKER_01] i sad je pitanje,

968
01:12:58,359 --> 01:13:00,060
[SPEAKER_01] znaš što to ljudi rade?

969
01:13:00,060 --> 01:13:01,119
[SPEAKER_01] Koja je poanta?

970
01:13:01,119 --> 01:13:02,579
[SPEAKER_01] Trebaš spavat.

971
01:13:02,579 --> 01:13:04,319
[SPEAKER_01] To uopće nema razgovora,

972
01:13:04,319 --> 01:13:05,060
[SPEAKER_01] da trebaš spavat.

973
01:13:05,859 --> 01:13:07,600
[SPEAKER_01] ako ti tijelo goreš spavat,

974
01:13:07,600 --> 01:13:09,079
[SPEAKER_01] ako ne možeš,

975
01:13:09,079 --> 01:13:10,340
[SPEAKER_01] jer moraš našto raditi,

976
01:13:10,340 --> 01:13:13,039
[SPEAKER_01] pa pokušaj kvalitetnu power nap imati.

977
01:13:13,039 --> 01:13:14,079
[SPEAKER_01] 20 minuta,

978
01:13:14,079 --> 01:13:16,579
[SPEAKER_01] bez da ti padne žlica iz ruke

979
01:13:16,579 --> 01:13:17,880
[SPEAKER_01] ili metalna kugla iz ruke.

980
01:13:19,600 --> 01:13:20,479
[SPEAKER_00] koliko se ja shvatio,

981
01:13:20,479 --> 01:13:21,659
[SPEAKER_00] zapravo nije poanta bila

982
01:13:21,659 --> 01:13:23,100
[SPEAKER_00] da se oni naspavaju,

983
01:13:23,100 --> 01:13:23,920
[SPEAKER_00] nego je poanta bila

984
01:13:23,920 --> 01:13:24,560
[SPEAKER_00] da se očito,

985
01:13:24,560 --> 01:13:26,300
[SPEAKER_00] možda ni valovi da odu

986
01:13:26,300 --> 01:13:27,060
[SPEAKER_00] u neku drugu

987
01:13:27,060 --> 01:13:29,460
[SPEAKER_00] frekvenciju.

988
01:13:29,460 --> 01:13:31,760
[SPEAKER_00] I onda su zapravo koristili

989
01:13:31,760 --> 01:13:33,520
[SPEAKER_00] tu tehniku kako bi

990
01:13:33,520 --> 01:13:35,739
[SPEAKER_00] možda bili intuitivni,

991
01:13:35,739 --> 01:13:37,100
[SPEAKER_00] dobivali bolje ideje,

992
01:13:37,100 --> 01:13:40,180
[SPEAKER_00] razmišljali o nekim problemima.

993
01:13:40,180 --> 01:13:40,960
[SPEAKER_01] Upravo si.

994
01:13:40,960 --> 01:13:41,560
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim da je

995
01:13:41,560 --> 01:13:42,399
[SPEAKER_01] kod ovoga slikara

996
01:13:42,399 --> 01:13:43,260
[SPEAKER_01] bila ideja

997
01:13:43,260 --> 01:13:44,800
[SPEAKER_01] nekakve kreativnosti

998
01:13:44,800 --> 01:13:45,239
[SPEAKER_01] ili nešto.

999
01:13:45,239 --> 01:13:46,279
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim da je bilo.

1000
01:13:46,279 --> 01:13:48,140
[SPEAKER_01] Ono što mogu kazao tome je da

1001
01:13:48,140 --> 01:13:50,380
[SPEAKER_01] nisam siguran li to točno.

1002
01:13:50,380 --> 01:13:51,859
[SPEAKER_01] Malo sam skeptičan

1003
01:13:51,859 --> 01:13:53,420
[SPEAKER_01] da će te činiti kreativnije

1004
01:13:53,420 --> 01:13:54,640
[SPEAKER_01] ako žlica padne sa stola,

1005
01:13:54,640 --> 01:13:55,760
[SPEAKER_01] jer imam osjećaj

1006
01:13:55,760 --> 01:13:56,779
[SPEAKER_01] da konstantno živimo

1007
01:13:56,779 --> 01:13:57,399
[SPEAKER_01] u nekoj buci

1008
01:13:57,399 --> 01:13:58,600
[SPEAKER_01] i onda da bi svi trebali

1009
01:13:58,600 --> 01:13:59,840
[SPEAKER_01] biti kreativi na taj način.

1010
01:13:59,840 --> 01:14:01,920
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da ja nisam siguran

1011
01:14:01,920 --> 01:14:03,340
[SPEAKER_01] da ima znanstvenih tvrnji za to,

1012
01:14:03,340 --> 01:14:04,319
[SPEAKER_01] ali nisam siguran,

1013
01:14:04,319 --> 01:14:06,020
[SPEAKER_01] pročitao sam to što si pročio,

1014
01:14:06,020 --> 01:14:07,819
[SPEAKER_01] ne znam je li to uopće točno

1015
01:14:07,819 --> 01:14:09,079
[SPEAKER_01] da su oni to radili.

1016
01:14:09,079 --> 01:14:10,340
[SPEAKER_01] Tako priče idu,

1017
01:14:10,340 --> 01:14:11,319
[SPEAKER_01] jer zašto kažem

1018
01:14:11,319 --> 01:14:12,239
[SPEAKER_01] čitao sam

1019
01:14:12,239 --> 01:14:13,659
[SPEAKER_01] i mislim da je bio

1020
01:14:13,659 --> 01:14:14,739
[SPEAKER_01] Einstein

1021
01:14:14,739 --> 01:14:17,180
[SPEAKER_01] da su bile isto priče

1022
01:14:17,180 --> 01:14:18,039
[SPEAKER_01] da je spavao,

1023
01:14:18,039 --> 01:14:18,739
